component.illusobjdesc:
Nine(?) figures, probably angels, hover right of God.  We see the lowermost figure from behind, but his head is twisted to the left so that we see his face in left profile.  
He is nude and has short, curly hair.  His arms are bent sharply upward at the elbows; his hands, with fingers spread, are raised with palms out (relative to his body).  His left leg is bent at the knee;  
his right leg may be slightly bent as well. His buttocks are prominent.
